{"title":"资助","icon":"subsidize","grey":true,"shareable":true,"id":"intro/subsidize/index","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"p","header":"关于资助","text":["作为一所倡导“尊重的教育”理念的师范大学，学校一直十分重视家庭经济困难学生的资助工作，构建了以国家助学贷款为主体，勤工助学为主导，“奖、贷、助、补、勤、减、免”七位一体的家庭经济困难学生资助工作体系，并成立了专门从事资助工作的机构——学生资助管理中心。所以即便您有经济困难，在收到大学录取通知书的时候，面对学费和生活费，也不必担心。"]},{"tag":"list","items":[{"text":"资助体系介绍","icon":"apartment","path":"intro/subsidize/intro"},{"text":"资助申请流程","icon":"subsidize-apply","path":"intro/subsidize/flow"},{"text":"资助计划","desc":"金额与人数","icon":"list","path":"intro/subsidize/plan"},{"text":"资助工作机构","icon":"office","path":"apartment/subsidize/index"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"助学贷款","items":[{"text":"国家助学贷款","icon":"loan","path":"intro/subsidize/loan/index"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"助学金","items":[{"text":"助学金","icon":"heart","path":"intro/subsidize/help/index"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"其他资助","items":[{"text":"入学绿色通道","icon":"green-tunnel","path":"intro/subsidize/green-tunnel/index"},{"text":"服兵役学生国家教育资助","icon":"military","path":"intro/subsidize/military/index"},{"text":"毕业生基层就业学费补偿","icon":"money","path":"intro/subsidize/reimburse"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"通知公告","items":[{"text":"2023 - 2024 学年资助对象评定","icon":"notice","path":"intro/subsidize/notice"}]}],"time":"2024 年 1 月 13 日 05:44:03"}